                            <comment id="14100368" author="sun.cheney" created="Mon, 18 Aug 2014 07:12:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I like to provide one patch for review.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch is rather straightforward, which add one option &quot;hbase.regionserver.use.ip&quot; to control whether to use ip or hostname in zookeeper. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By default, the value is false, to leave the current behavior unchanged. If set the value to true, regionserver ip instead of its hostname registered under the HBASE_ROOT/rs/ip.xx.xxx.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
